name: - Bird's eye view of Langtang Gomba (Nepal series #30) -
description:
View from the summit of Cherko Ri (5000m). While climbing this mountain, I had to stop a few times. I got the altitude sickness. I was not very well prepared for this last hike. I felt a bit dizzy and had to slow down my pace. I reached the summit last in the group, but I did not care. I was so proud that I had not given up and was rewarded with this fantastic view.

5616px X 3744px
